ed in this group are our european companies specialists we offer fullservice corporate and investment banking and capital markets product capabilities offered through the following departments corporate and investment banking the corporate and investment banking group in mexico includes traditional services such as corporate and investment products corporate lending and loan syndications equity and debt underwriting and mergers and acquisitions all product specialists within this group work together as a team to deliver integrated solutions to clients needs that best match their needs and capitalize on opportunities available to them these product specialists also work across a number of industries to deliver specialized knowledge of the industry context in which a given company operates global equity sales and trading the global equity sales and trading group in mexico represents an integrated area dealing with debt and equity capital markets sales and trading services and institutional sales our traders have built solid relationships with the institutional buyside through a professional approach and understanding each clients portfolio and trading style the trading desk offers a fullservice approach from idea generation to execution foreign exchange in mexico our foreign exchange group is responsible for clients monetary exchange needs in the mexican market as well as managing foreign exchange risk exposure for clients the group coordinates local coverage with our global fx team headquartered in toronto to provide outstanding service and innovative products to clients in mexico derivatives sales in mexico our derivatives group provides innovative investment and risk management solutions according to a clients risk profile we design protection from fluctuating exchange and interest rates as well as from market risk through various hedging strategies our products and services include interest rate swaps crosscurrency interest rate swaps exchange rate futures forwards and options future rate agreements interest rate options caps floors collars derivatives listed on the mexican derivatives market futures and options on stocks and indices as well as advice to manage and diversify risks through other areas of scotiabank clients in mexico also have access to a full range of cash management trade finance and correspondent banking trust services and treasury services our ability to also service clients in canada and the us allows us to provide total nafta coverage for corporate institutional and government clients both domestic and local affiliates of multinational companies ways to contact us to find out more about scotiabank products and services available in mexico please contact locations mexico city monterrey guadalajara plaza scotiabank inverlat mexico blvd manuel a camacho no  col lomas de chapultepec mexico df cp  t  f  plaza scotiabank inverlat monterrey av lázaro cárdenas no  pte col residencial san agustin san pedro garza garcía nl cp  t  f  plaza scotiabank inverlat guadalajara prolongación américas no  col providencia guadalajara jal cp  t  f  latin america and the caribbean bahamas scotiabank has a local office in nassau bahamas and offers offshore booking for derivative and global fixed income products through our global banking and markets division we can also provide clients with access to other corporate and investment banking and capital markets products and services in addition we offer a range of cash management and trade finance services through other areas of scotiabank for more information please visit our local bahamas website ways to contact us locations nassau suite  centre of commerce one bay street po box n nassau bahamas t  f  to find out more about scotiabank products and services available in the bahamas please contact david wayne howard director scotiabank caribbean treasury t   brazil scotiabank has operated in brazil with a representative office since the early s providing trade finance and correspo